title: YouTube Bows to the WHO! | Ep #11 Good Morning Mug Club
description: Talking Susan Wojcicki's interview with Brian Stelter and Youtube's bowing to WHO, calling BS on CNN's coverage of the press briefing, and some new updates on COVID death rates. We also check in with our team in the office and Steven gives some inside baseball about the time he met Clint Eastwood.
